dataIdInfo.idPurp: This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data. [This data layer is for use in generalized mapping applications. The data layer is intended for use with GIS software.]
dataIdInfo.idAbs: This data layer represents municipalities for Marinette County, Wisconsin in 2014. [The municipal boundary feature class represents the civil/municipal boundaries in Marinette County, Wisconsin. Data is referenced to the Marinette County Coordinate System, North American Datum 1983 with the 1991 adjustment (NAD83/91).]
